hierarchical cluster

df2 <- scale(df[,2:4])
d <- dist(df2, method = "euclidean")
hc1 <- hclust(d, method = "complete" )
plot(hc1, cex = 0.6, hang = -1)

hc5 <- hclust(d, method = "ward.D2" )

# Cut tree into 4 groups
sub_grp <- cutree(hc5, k = 4)
